 />\n其實方文山嘅詞真係入心入肺</blockquote><br />\n明明就　明明就　明明就<br />\n他比較溫柔　也許他能給你更多<br />\n不用抉擇　我會自動變朋友"},{"pid":"db18c28b0100f9c85f21b890e61b8a9e711d748e","tid":434583,"uid":42419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:16:10.000Z","msg":"爽歪的麻雀"},{"pid":"ff159af9f60182dc1d8552966f9a401c73803991","tid":434583,"uid":34934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:18:43.000Z","msg":"天涼了　雨下了　妳走了<br />\n清楚了　我愛的　遺失了<br />\n落葉飄在湖面上睡著了<br />\n<br />\n想要放　放不掉　淚在飄<br />\n妳看看　妳看看不到<br />\n我假裝過去不重要<br />\n卻發現自己辦不到"},{"pid":"ba2e3911c6a944dc2c1a72d55daa41d11c425e3d","tid":434583,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:21:06.000Z","msg":"說了再見　才發現再也見不到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06300d799cff9a667894d947e21e5fe8e034d5ea","tid":434583,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:25:16.000Z","msg":"最長的電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554cbcdad0f8df2bb077a60d3574877c009bf778","tid":434583,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>稻香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhi Ben <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLaB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d50906b0bd90d6bc6dd816ddf52852bc3f21ba","tid":434583,"uid":120848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:28:02.000Z","msg":"有冇人想聽我唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01feecf1f0f6222c023af21c094710bd787a1584","tid":434583,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:29:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>稻香<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm