話<br />\n<br />\n長大後我開始明白<br />\n為什麼我跑得比別人快 飛得比別人高<br />\n將來大家看的都是我畫的漫畫 <span style=\"color: red;\">大家唱的都是我寫的歌</span><br />\n媽媽的辛苦不讓你看見 溫暖的食譜在她心裡面<br />\n有空就多多握握她的手 把手牽著一起夢遊<br />\n聽媽媽的話 別讓她受傷 想快快長大 才能保護她<br />\n美麗的白髮 幸福中發芽 天使的魔法 溫暖中慈祥"},{"pid":"ed4991434473ebb9906420555bd1088ccb941d94","tid":434583,"uid":1184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:39:53.000Z","msg":"駛乜講"},{"pid":"49b3a292eadbd1a00a8f64a0f0ad2a271065027d","tid":434583,"uid":36712,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:40:54.000Z","msg":"天灰灰　會不會　讓我忘了你是誰<br />\n夜越黑　夢違背　難追難回味<br />\n我的世界將被摧毀　也許事與願違"},{"pid":"077a7bdd055b3f8d58eea302328dcd7806d11567","tid":434583,"uid":96732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:41:36.000Z","msg":"楓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07232addbb8ae1cb1cf81172a9b76e3285a3141a","tid":434583,"uid":147972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:43:20.000Z","msg":"我不落淚 忍住感覺<br />\n分手在起風 這個季節...<br />\n哭久了會累<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca47d555d8301fbfabfd1655d791bbf6e96c3e00","tid":434583,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:45:11.000Z","msg":"抽屜泛黃的日記 榨乾了回憶<br />\n那笑容 是夏季 妳我的過去被順時針的忘記<br />\n缺氧過後的愛情 粗心的眼淚是多餘"},{"pid":"1355dd37179b751743fdd7f9621ba5690b36977f","tid":434583,"uid":120848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今晚開個tg channel唱比你地聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n企開d啦屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n話唔定好聽呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167bb2982c3303838065f7aea83ce7edbe874d6c","tid":434583,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote